arts.ttl: Millwall hit back to deny 10-player Charlton
arts.sum: Ra'ees Bangura Williams' 88th-minute goal earned Millwall a 1-1 draw at The Valley and denied Charlton a first victory over their south London rivals in 29 years.

arts.ttl: Championship weekend predictions for all 12 games
arts.sum: LiveScore makes its picks for the weekend action as Middlesbrough set the pace while Coventry prove to be the most lethal in front of goal.
